Paper: hep-th/0203158

Date: 2002-03-18

Title: Discussing the Spectrum of the Kalb-Ramond Field Coupled to 3D-Gravity

Authors: J.L. Boldo, J.A. Helayel-Neto and N. Panza

Comments: 9 pages, 2 figures

The mechanism of dynamical mass generation for the gauge field is studiedthrough 1-loop. We find out that torsion is an obstruction to the appearance ofa 1-loop mass correction. Contrary, if torsion is not present, a mass gap isgenerated for the 2-form field.